Dear {!Lead.FirstName},
It was good to talk with you today. I would like to take this opportunity to introduce Astrum Solar further to you.
THE ASTRUM SOLAR DIFFERENCE
Astrum Solar makes sure you get the most out of your solar panels: the most energy generated, the most electricity savings, the most beneficial environmental impact and the most joy and pride each time you see a sunny day.
Astrum Solar, the leading full-service residential solar provider headquartered in the Eastern U.S., provides a premier customer experience. We offer cutting edge technology, nothing out-of-pocket lease and purchasing options and superior client service at every stage of your transition to solar electricity.
Free Solar Installation
Think solar is beyond your budget? Think again. Pay nothing to start and watch your solar energy savings pile up over the lifetime of your system.
Attached to this e-mail you'll find a detailed overview of what our company has to offer.
Of course you can always find us on the web at www.astrumsolar.com
